      <title>欧洲天然气价格波动性较低，表明交易员应避免大举押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/low-volatility-in-european-gas-signals-traders-avoiding-big-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年欧洲天然气期权的波动性有所下降，表明在最近的供应中断凸显该地区天然气供应的脆弱性后，交易商正在避免进行大额押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/low-volatility-in-european-gas-signals-traders-avoiding-big-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 08:01:47 GMT</pubDate>
